EYWA PROTOCOL

EYWA is a truly decentralized cross-chain data transfer environment and a revolutionary solution to the liquidity problem of cross-chain bridges, creating aggregated cross-chain assets. We are creating tools for building a new generation of dApps - we continue the evolution from multichain dApps to crosschain, simplifying the user experience, bringing a billion users to DeFi.
